{"type":"assistant","message":{"model":"claude-opus-4-6","id":"msg_011FKnvcDHXRgjpc2STE9DnG","type":"message","role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"The fix is correct. The two bugs were:\n\n1. **`Config[\"prompt\"]`** stores `file(\".cloche/prompts/implement.md\")` but the handler was trying to use that entire string as a file path. Fixed by extracting the path from the `file(\"...\")` wrapper before reading.\n\n2. **Script steps** use `Config[\"run\"]` (e.g., `run = \"go test ./... 2>&1\"`) but the handler was looking for `Config[\"command\"]` and `Config[\"script\"]`, which don't exist. Fixed to check `Config[\"run\"]`.\n\nAlso updated the drawer UI JavaScript to display the `run` config key instead of the non-existent `command`/`script` keys.\n\nCLOCHE_RESULT:success"}],"stop_reason":null,"stop_sequence":null,"usage":{"input_tokens":1,"cache_creation_input_tokens":429,"cache_read_input_tokens":41458,"cache_creation":{"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens":0,"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens":429},"output_tokens":1,"service_tier":"standard","inference_geo":"not_available"},"context_management":null},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"287f3a27-118f-4f7e-b0f1-0e7789c0a986","uuid":"e034cc0a-016b-437d-be8c-3fee169adea5"}
